 # Trading Stack
 
+## Bitget MCP + CCXT Setup
+
+This stack uses the `wolfcubecho/ccxt` fork for Bitget integration. Ensure the dependency is present and MCP Bitget Trading is installed:
+
+```bash
+npm install github:wolfcubecho/ccxt
+cd mcp/MCP-bitget-trading
+npm install
+npm test --silent
+```
+
+### Demo vs Live
+
+- Demo (paper): set `BITGET_SANDBOX=true` and provide demo keys
+- Live (mainnet): set `BITGET_SANDBOX=false` and provide live keys
+
+On Windows PowerShell:
+
+```powershell
+$env:BITGET_API_KEY = "<your_live_key>"
+$env:BITGET_SECRET_KEY = "<your_live_secret>"
+$env:BITGET_PASSPHRASE = "<your_live_passphrase>"
+$env:BITGET_SANDBOX = "false"
+```
